{"tid":2389323,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–癌細胞轉移後所產生的變化","createTime":"2021-01-31T22:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T12:35:39.000Z","uid":38861,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2652d7d3589ee725ab615ff03635d87c38815247","tid":2389323,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T22:17:29.000Z","msg":"癌細胞的新陳代謝與普通細胞有著顯著的分別，原因是癌細胞需要截然不同的新陳代謝來滿足生長的需要。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7x2H4mO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7x2H4mO.jpg&h=d3423184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但是，當癌細胞從原有位置轉移到另一位置後，其新陳代謝有會否有所轉變呢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）mTORC1是其中一隻掌管細胞生長的蛋白質，而有研究(Ref1)指出，從乳癌轉移到肺部的癌細胞，其mTORC1所帶來的效果更為強大，能令癌細胞生長得更快。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0f3zVtw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0f3zVtw.jpg&h=9094e733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）科學家發現，肺部含有充足的Pyruvate代謝物，而利用藥物阻擋「乳癌轉移過來的肺癌」吸收Pyruvate的話，便能減低mTORC1的功效。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrJHjVd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrJHjVd.jpg&h=a4641434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但奇怪的是，用藥物阻擋原發腫瘤乳癌吸收Pyruvate的話，mTORC1的功效並不會有所減低，腫瘤生長的速度並無任何特別變化。<br />\n<br />\n這顯示出，癌細胞從原有地方轉移到另一位置後，其新陳代謝亦有著顯著的變化。<br />\n這有可能是因為第二處位置的生長環境有所不同，故此癌細胞需要調節其新陳代謝來適應新環境。<br />\n<br />\n在乳癌轉移到肺部的癌細胞，我們可透過針對Pyruvate的吸收來減慢他們的生長，但這是否只適用於從其他位置轉移到肺部的癌細胞，以及乳癌轉移到其他位置的癌細胞，那還需要進一步的研究確實。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=95c162d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=d1c523aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於WhatsApp/Facebook等問題，IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1097276520308273\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS1097276520308273&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=22d535d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1097276520308273</a>"},{"pid":"8d13f7f13bf59d9b9649b5b87a996175a4768661","tid":2389323,"uid":34119,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/editors/11975/20180824161600_5b7fbec056779.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Feditors%2F11975%2F20180824161600_5b7fbec056779.jpg&h=e56223d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d67f1d31cfe86cbeaf00f761fda4a5dcc235060f","tid":2389323,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:17:02.000Z","msg":"咁早出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8f57ccaed71cac83ff8cb84b1dda938c0d36fc","tid":2389323,"uid":145273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:23:14.000Z","m